reviews.text: A very nice coffee shop with chill environment. Coffee and donuts are very good! Morning time they serve breakast with eggs, bacon and bread. It is a relax area at Nathan Road. One thing is not good that the shop is very small so there are not many tables.

I would be inclined to give J.Co a high rating because of its price and halal option. Regardless, J.Co offers great donuts and coffees are definitely inviting. Check it out if you want grest food for your buck.
our group favorite doughnut.. take away doughnut, and spend breakfast with friends 😍 we love j. co

How conflict with the statement on the tissues ? As a customer in hurry city, the barista ran behind me for stopping to toilet. He means no customer cannot in toilet. Manager keep asking about take away or dine in in order to pushing you speed up in closing which instead of gently remind . Even though lack of good service,  all material in recipe is less coffee beans to maintain the bussiness. How poor the stores is still alive in competitive city? Ridiculous!
Ignore Americans and wait on locals leaving you standing there.  We rose above the discrimination and ordered.  Donuts and green tea latte very good.

reviews.text:
Bon cafè. Gran varietat de donuts i d'entrepans. Lloc tranquil per esmorzar o berenar, amb música de fons relaxant.
(A la imatge, donut de crema de cacahuet amb cobertura de xocolata blanca i café espresso doble.)
休閒歇一歇好地方🥰，新出😍Pandan 咖啡☕️😘
食物買相吸引，略嫌法包不夠硬身
簡錢合理， 甜甜圈甜度適中。 推薦
話明係度飲，沖杯紙杯，我話轉瓦杯佢話唔夠人手洗杯，但係有好多個乾淨杯係部機上面，作為一間cafe都唔知瓦杯飲同紙杯飲會對杯咖啡既味相差很遠都唔在乎。仲有包包糖都受潮。第一次黎，舖面唔錯服務同質素⋯⋯
